parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS can cause extended stopping distances, loss of control, and increased risk of accidents, which can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The ABS light comes on and stays on
the brake pedal goes to the floor
the vehicle takes longer to stop
the vehicle surges forward when applying the brakes
the brakes make noise
and the brakes fail without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake master cylinder can cause the brake pedal to go to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to stop the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal goes to the floor
the brake pedal does not return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
and the vehicle is unable to stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake hydraulic system can cause the brake pedal to go to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to stop the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal goes to the floor
the brake pedal does not return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
and the vehicle is unable to stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake Pedal and Accelerator Pedal Interference
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The close proximity of the brake pedal and accelerator pedal can cause unintended acceleration, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The foot touches the accelerator pedal when applying the brakes
causing the vehicle to surge forward.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine stalling or failure can cause loss of power, steering, and braking, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine stalls without warning
the vehicle suddenly stops
the engine catches on fire
the vehicle loses power
difficulty steering or stopping
steam coming from the front of the vehicle
and no brakes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of engine components can cause engine stalling or failure, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Piece out of crankshaft
destroyed connecting rod
crankshaft timing pickup sensor failure
engine mount failure
motor mounts broke
and water pump failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine fires can cause damage to the vehicle, injuries, and even fatalities.
symptoms: The engine catches on fire
smoke coming from the engine compartment
and the vehicle is engulfed in flames.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission oil cooler line can cause transmission fluid to leak onto the hot engine, leading to a fire in the engine compartment, which can result in vehicle damage or even injury.
symptoms: Transmission fluid leaking onto the engine
smoke rolling out from under the car
transmission fluid spraying onto the hot engine
transmission fluid leaking onto the ground
transmission fluid leak noticed during regular maintenance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission cooling unit can cause transmission fluid to leak onto the hot engine, leading to a fire in the engine compartment, which can result in vehicle damage or even injury.
symptoms: Transmission fluid leaking onto the engine
smoke rolling out from under the car
transmission fluid spraying onto the hot engine
transmission fluid leaking onto the ground
transmission fluid leak noticed during regular maintenance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the shift solenoid can cause the shift lever to malfunction, leading to difficulty shifting gears, which can result in loss of vehicle control or accidents.
symptoms: Shift lever stuck in park
difficulty shifting gears
shift lever malfunctioning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission axle seal can cause transmission fluid to leak, leading to premature wear on transmission components and potentially causing transmission failure.
symptoms: Transmission fluid leaking onto the ground
transmission fluid leak noticed during regular maintenance.
